  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0db1\u0dba\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0ddc\u0dba\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd4\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An operation to find the elephant that crashed into Jackson's vehicle",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior officer of the Anuradhapura Assistant Director's Office of the Department of Wildlife Conservation said that two teams have been deployed to search for the wild elephant that collided with the cab in which veteran actor Jackson Anthony was traveling.",
        "He also said that it is believed that the wild elephant may have been seriously injured as the wild elephant landed twice on the bonnet of the vehicle when it collided with the cab in which three people including Mr. Jackson Anthony were traveling on the night of the 2nd at around 10.30 p.m. near the Seventh Post in Talawa Moragoda.",
        "Accordingly, two teams consisting of officers working in Anuradhapura and Talawa offices are engaged in a search operation to search for this wild elephant in Ulukkulam and Wiraveva areas of Moragoda area.",
        "The senior officer of the Anuradhapura Assistant Director's Office of the Wildlife Conservation Department added that no information has been received so far regarding the elephant that collided with the vehicle."
      ],
